nodes.bodyText:
Suggested change
        
          
    

        
      
    
    
      
          
            
            		// Map<ReceiptScheduleId, ReceiptScheduleExternalInfo> externalInfoByScheduleId = null;
from this javadoc, i guess NONE should rather be named CURRENT_DATE or TODAY, wdyt?
here you could use (CoalesceUtils.)coalesce(externalInfoByReceiptScheduleId, ImmutableMap.of()), in my mind that's more readable

Suggested change * Calls {@link #InOutProducer(InOutGenerateResult, boolean, ReceiptMovementDateRule, Map)} with ReceiptMovementDateRule.NONE && externalInfoByScheduleId = null. * Calls {@link #InOutProducer(InOutGenerateResult, boolean, ReceiptMovementDateRule, Map)} with ReceiptMovementDateRule.CURRENT_DATE && externalInfoByScheduleId = null.
